        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Years ago, Si Teng, a plant-alien hybrid, was hunted down and killed by a Xuanmen hunter in Shanghai. Her remains were buried at the base of a cliff, but fate intervened when architect Qin Fang unknowingly resurrected her. Confused and seeking answers, Si Teng demands Qin’s help to recover her memories and adapt to the modern world. As they grow closer, Si Teng struggles with her past, and their quest for answers\n\nbrings them face-to-face with a demon that refuses to die.",
